| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0742 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 28a2f3d5-465b-5dd9-a9cb-55340ad14cd6"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
